b'{"data_headers":{"result_code":1},"data":{"information":{"article_id":975,"category_name":"News","pr_category_id":"1","title_name":"Adding the Mana Spiral to More Adventurers!","message":"<div><span style=\\"color: rgb(41, 105, 176);\\"><strong>[Addendum <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1580094000\\"><\/span>]<\/strong><\/span><br>The issue where the displayed Might value did not increase after unlocking the &quot;Advanced Training&quot; node of the mana spiral was fixed in version 1.16.0, so the Might values displayed in this notification have been updated.<br>After updating to version 1.16.0, the Might value with 70 mana nodes unlocked will be as shown in this notification.<br>Note: Only the displayed Might value has changed. The power of standard attacks has not been changed.<\/div><hr><div><br><\/div><div>A sixth mana circle, the mana spiral, will be added to a certain adventurer starting <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1577772000\\"><\/span>.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>The adventurer affected this time and his stats are described below.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Affected Adventurers<\/div><div>5\\u2605 Ieyasu (shadow\/blade)<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Stats<\/div><div>\\u30fb5\\u2605 adventurer<\/div><div>\\n<div class=\\"summonPickUp adjust\\">\\n<div class=\\"thumbList\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"thumbnail\\">\\n\\t\\t<img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/990f697a3329181a0f88b8d991c3276a2.png\\">\\n\\t\\t<img class=\\"rarity\\" src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/23b8fc2cd656aa0d5ef96984f257ce7e2.png\\">\\n\\t<\/div>\\n\\t<div class=\\"discription\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"charaName\\">Ieyasu<\/div><\/div>\\n<\/div>\\n\\n\\t<div class=\\"status\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Stats<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"param\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"base\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"lv\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<spa