tion\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Co-abilities<\/div>\\n\\t<dl>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/87595b7438e74e5502d8b830d6bd16832.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Strength +10%<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tIncreases strength by 10%.<br>Benefits your whole team.\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dd>\\n\\t<\/dl><\/div><div class=\\"ability explanation\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Abilities<\/div>\\n\\t<dl><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/25ef50e0a0cfce84d2ec98ed78c188702.png\\"><\/span><span>HP 70% = Critical Rate +13%<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Increases critical rate by 13% when<br>HP is 70% or above.<\/div><\/dd><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/760d630739a2cdfb77dad15b5985557d2.png\\"><\/span><span>Potent Paralysis Res +100%<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Reduces susceptibility to paralysis by 100%.<br>When the user is hit by an attack that would have<br>paralyzed them, their strength is increased by 15%<br>for 10 seconds. After activating, this buff will not<br>activate again for 15 seconds.<\/div><\/dd><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/a9a2062688b0dab674737420e3f389b72.png\\"><\/span><span>Critical Damage +30%<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Adds 30% to the modifier applied to critical damage.<\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div><\/div><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Notes:<\/div><div>1. The stats shown here represent the adventurer at level 100 with 70 mana nodes unbound.<\/div><div>2. The stats shown here do not include increases or decreases due to abilities.<\/div><div>3. The stats for the adventurer included in this notification shown in any prior notifications or preview videos were the stats at level 80 with 50 mana nodes unbound.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div>","start_time":1577685600,"prev_article_id":"952","next_article_id":"964","image_path":"","update_time":1580095325}}}'